    public interface NamedSBase
extends SBase
    Base class for all the SBML components with an id and a name (optional or not) in SBML Level 3 Version 1 or lower. Since SBML Level 3 Version 2, every SBase have an id an a name. This interface is kept as it is to be able to know which elements could have an id or name before SBML L3V2, not every SBase will be NamedSBase in jsbml. If you support L3V2 and want to manipulate id and name, prefer to use the SBase interface instead of NamedSBase.
    Since:
    0.8
    Author:
    Andreas Dräger, marine
